            <bug_when>2011-09-06 14:34:00 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>For test development, it would be useful to load the Testrunner with e.g. a URI parameter that instructs it to immediately run the entire suite of tests without waiting for the user to click the &quot;Run&quot; button. Combined with the &quot;testclass&quot; parameter that restricts the test namespace, this could speed up the modify/reload/run development cycle.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
